{"type": "article", "id": 23935, "title": "可串水果的水杯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-16T07:00:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 138, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144108pHoO81WE9AscFX3B.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这款水杯带有一根轴心，它是用来串水果的。它针对人们喜欢浸泡水果喝水的习惯，将不同的水果串在上面，以方便均匀地浸泡。此外，将不同的水果串在上面也增加了瓶子本身的装饰性。它还有漏塞等配件，可以替换或完全不使用。这个设计获得了日本 GOOD DESIGN 和 2016 年 IF 奖，即将上市。<a href=\"http://www.3plus1creation.com/wp/news/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144106qey2DAiIzMa57CKS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.70761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144107El971RAykeSfZxrP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144107V94wJcWYO1ukKse7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}